      • BugReport

        public BugReport(int id,
                 User reporter,
                 User resolver,
                 java.lang.String application,
                 java.lang.String location,
                 java.lang.String description,
                 java.lang.String steps,
                 java.lang.String severity,
                 java.util.Date date,
                 java.lang.String status)
        Constructs BugReport with a resolver.

        This constructor creates a BugReport with both a resolver and reporter, this is used for when a BugReport is resolved by a user.

        Parameters:
        id - id of BugReport for the Database
        reporter - user that submitted BugReport
        resolver - user that fixed the bug in the program
        application - name of project the bug was found in
        location - location of bug in the document
        description - description of the bug problem
        steps - steps required to solve bug
        severity - ranking of how important the bug is that needs to be fixed
        date - date of creation of report
        status - current status of report by default pending

        Constructs BugReport without a resolver.

        This constructor creates a BugReport without a resolver and reporter, this is used for creating a completely new BugReport for submission.

        Parameters:
        id - id of BugReport for the Database
        reporter - user that submitted BugReport
        application - name of project the bug was found in
        location - location of bug in the document
        description - description of the bug problem
        steps - steps required to solve bug
        severity - ranking of how important the bug is that needs to be fixed
        date - date of creation of report
        status - current status of report by default pending
